  "id": "BIT-golang-2023-54365",
  "summary": "Traefik - Denial of Service via HTTP/2 Request Handling",
  "details": "Traefik before 2.10.5 and 3.0.0 is affected by a denial-of-service vulnerability in HTTP/2 request handling inherited from the Go standard library's HTTP/2 implementation (CVE-2023-44487 / CVE-2023-39325, the 'Rapid Reset' technique). A remote attacker can rapidly create and cancel HTTP/2 streams to exhaust server resources and cause service unavailability.",
